  <summary date="2017-02-01T05:00:00Z" status="Introduced in Senate">Protecting Seniors' Access to Medicare Act of 2017

This bill amends&#160;the Patient Protection and Affordable Care Act (PPACA) to terminate the Independent Payment Advisory Board (IPAB). Under PPACA,&#160;the IPAB is tasked with developing proposals to reduce the per capital rate of growth in Medicare spending.</summary>
